Comment: 0,0:00:00.95,0:00:00.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,==========OP==========
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.14,0:02:09.31,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是连前进轨道都无法改变的几率
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.31,0:02:13.82,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,只要有百分之一就要奋起反抗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.82,0:02:17.65,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟、被「命运」所束缚的人生、不 我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.65,0:02:24.33,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,我要将它重写、因为若能看见你和未来 不是最棒吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.33,0:02:27.45,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧！我只想在战斗中成长 HEY!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.45,0:02:28.29,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,击穿阴天！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.29,0:02:31.46,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,我的烈焰仍旧熊熊燃烧 雷鸣撕裂天空
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.46,0:02:35.30,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,我只想消除梦魇 看见未来！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.30,0:02:37.76,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,过去、未来、还有如今当下、
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.76,0:02:40.76,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,我不畏惧过去 现在为了被托付的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.76,0:02:42.09,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,我要吼出我的骄傲!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.09,0:02:48.77,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,因为不想看到眼泪、所以要不断嘶吼！一直永远…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.77,0:02:52.77,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会堕落！因为扬起的风会让我凌驾于命运之上！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.77,0:02:59.15,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,因为身后、有着想要守护的笑容！ 永远…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.15,0:03:02.62,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,为了彼此！我会揍飞你心中的痛苦！让悲伤什么的永远安息！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.66,0:03:06.74,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,832)}无论多少次…
Comment: 0,0:00:00.95,0:00:00.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,==========ED==========
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.99,0:22:34.91,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,月光摇曳 我们未来的蓝图
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.91,0:22:42.17,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,总有一天会实现 描绘明天吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.92,0:22:46.96,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,永远不会磨灭 铭记在心中的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.96,0:22:55.77,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,若是无尽的泪水能掩盖伤痕
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.77,0:23:04.82,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,那就无需畏惧 再次去相信吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.82,0:23:13.28,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,向着无边无际的天空 张开双臂
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.28,0:23:19.12,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,为了不再哭泣 仰望天空中那轮皎月
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.12,0:23:24.96,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,即使心存悲伤 也要怀着希望
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.96,0:23:29.30,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,就算无法回头 也没有关系
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.30,0:23:35.93,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,熠熠生辉的梦想 闪耀在探索的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.93,0:23:41.94,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,最宝贵的那份思念 仍旧在延续
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.94,0:23:47.78,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,无论哪里 我们都一起走过
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.78,0:23:55.58,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,825)}握住那唯一的心灵之匙吧
Comment: 0,0:00:00.95,0:00:00.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,==========Avant==========
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.36,0:00:09.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,公主 这里就交给魔法师们
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.23,0:00:09.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们先撤退吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.49,0:00:12.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也来负责护送
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.82,0:00:15.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 请让我留在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.57,0:00:18.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有看到最后的义务
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.45,0:00:20.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,公主…但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.87,0:00:21.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.25,0:00:26.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个 请看看这个
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.88,0:00:28.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.42,0:00:30.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是未来的我所留下的笔记本
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.84,0:00:31.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,未来的…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.88,0:00:33.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请看这里
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.51,0:00:42.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,万一这个时代的大门遭到破坏
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.27,0:00:45.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么未来的日蚀之门也会不复存在
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.15,0:00:49.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连锁反应下 我的存在也会被抹消
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.23,0:00:50.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.82,0:00:55.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说 如果现在这个时代的大门被破坏掉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.74,0:01:00.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么未来也会被改写成「大门已经被破坏的未来」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.58,0:01:03.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,未来也就不会有大门存在了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.21,0:01:07.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果那样 罗格就没有办法来到这个时代了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.88,0:01:11.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…这能够阻止已经发生了的事情吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.50,0:01:12.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,顺利的话
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.76,0:01:15.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龙和罗格都会从这个时代消失
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.80,0:01:17.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,值得一试
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.72,0:01:20.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是有个大问题
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.06,0:01:24.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要怎么破坏那么巨大的建筑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.68,0:01:26.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是个轻松的活儿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.02,0:01:29.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是如果罗格没从未来过来的话
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.81,0:01:32.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个世界就会回到原本的历史轨迹上
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.53,0:01:34.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只能这么做了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.19,0:01:38.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使是为了遵守和未来的我的约定
Comment: 0,0:00:00.95,0:00:00.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,==========Main==========
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.09,0:03:19.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要把仅存的魔力都用上哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.26,0:03:20.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.97,0:03:26.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打开吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.26,0:03:28.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十二门的守护者
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.56,0:03:31.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黄道十二宫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.83,0:03:53.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家 拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.77,0:04:20.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会…毫无效果
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.82,0:04:24.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它是用超强抗魔力耐性的超魔力合金制成的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.36,0:04:27.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能这么简单就被破坏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.62,0:04:29.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算如此
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.95,0:04:35.79,Title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3\pos(640,450)\fad(524,0}黄金草原
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.31,0:04:55.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伽吉鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.24,0:05:08.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快从我们的时代…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.16,0:05:11.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,滚回去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.75,0:05:14.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没打算回去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.87,0:05:17.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 现在的罗格怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.75,0:05:20.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总有一天 我会和我成为一体
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.13,0:05:23.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就如同影子和影子重叠一样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.71,0:05:25.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你打算剥夺罗格的未来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.01,0:05:27.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根本没有未来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.18,0:05:30.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要有阿库诺罗基亚在
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.27,0:05:36.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我才会来这里创造未来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.46,0:06:41.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弗洛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.09,0:06:44.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.96,0:06:46.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他活着
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.13,0:06:52.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在 在这个瞬间 他一定很慌张
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.93,0:06:54.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.85,0:06:59.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有关系的 有我在你身边
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.39,0:07:03.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会死的 反正一年后也会死
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.15,0:07:04.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没有保护他吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.11,0:07:07.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是没能保护
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.19,0:07:10.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在他还是活着的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.66,0:07:16.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无所谓了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.54,0:07:20.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经不是只会陪猫玩的那个我了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.71,0:07:23.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.21,0:07:27.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有品尝过绝望的家伙是无法理解的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.55,0:07:32.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道得到这个千载难逢的希望后 我有多么疯狂吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.47,0:07:36.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的希望…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.77,0:07:41.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是让过去被绝望笼罩吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.77,0:07:48.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能让所有的人都得到幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.57,0:07:52.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成熟点吧 夏·多拉格尼尔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.61,0:07:55.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是事实如此
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.16,0:07:58.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁都有选择未来的资格
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.58,0:08:03.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们 要继续我们所选择的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.79,0:08:06.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而不是你选择的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.96,0:08:09.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.97,0:08:14.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天会怎样 就算不知道也无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.47,0:08:19.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了竭尽全力活在现在
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.06,0:00:00.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.04,0:08:42.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.04,0:08:44.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.03,0:09:16.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让你久等了啊 露西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.32,0:09:18.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.78,0:09:20.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你们听好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.24,0:09:23.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要得意忘形了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.20,0:09:28.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是妖精的尾巴的魔法师 夏·多拉格尼尔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.84,0:09:31.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是一名灭龙魔法师
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.72,0:09:42.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火龙的煌炎 咆哮
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.81,0:09:46.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火龙碎牙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.52,0:09:53.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏  已经…无计可施了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.07,0:09:56.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才没有那种事 一定还有办法的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.75,0:10:07.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.58,0:10:12.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对…不会放弃的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.25,0:10:17.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会逃 也不会退缩
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.09,0:10:22.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还远远…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.60,0:10:24.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有结束…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.72,0:10:26.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.78,0:10:36.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经没有办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.61,0:10:39.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,极限了…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.63,0:10:58.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这大门也太结实了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.67,0:11:01.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到这样都毫发无损
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.05,0:11:04.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.72,0:11:08.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快离开
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.89,0:11:11.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家快离开大门
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.49,0:12:49.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大门被破坏掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.45,0:12:50.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.09,0:13:06.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难以置信…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.93,0:13:09.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然将超魔力合金的门给…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.39,0:13:11.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这之后会怎么样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.56,0:13:15.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根据计算 未来的门会变得无法使用
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.48,0:13:18.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说 罗格无法来到这个时代
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.69,0:13:20.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,历史会恢复原状
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.49,0:13:30.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龙的身体…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.74,0:13:31.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发出了光
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.00,0:13:39.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要回到原来的时代了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.56,0:13:53.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要卷起尾巴逃走了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.35,0:13:56.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不对…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.77,0:14:00.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.86,0:14:01.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龙都…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.27,0:14:03.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在消失？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.94,0:14:09.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,区区人类 区区人类
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.41,0:14:16.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.87,0:14:19.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样很危险的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.54,0:14:20.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.75,0:14:28.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,建造了连接时空之门的是我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.59,0:14:33.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,扰乱了各位自然时间的流动
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.06,0:14:42.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你生活在400年前 而我们生活在现在
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.36,0:14:47.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本来应该是毫无争斗理由的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.53,0:14:52.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而将此扭曲了的正是我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.24,0:14:55.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是什么人？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.20,0:14:59.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,翡翠·E·费欧雷
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.33,0:15:00.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,翡翠？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.67,0:15:05.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 和你的身体颜色一样的翡翠
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.46,0:15:09.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说…一样？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.13,0:15:11.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.89,0:15:16.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,翡翠之龙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.72,0:15:21.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,翡翠之龙…听上去挺不错的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.90,0:15:24.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不对 等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.81,0:15:27.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 被蒙过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.40,0:15:29.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,898)}我是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.35,0:16:01.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搞定…了吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.44,0:16:08.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉好像成功了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.15,0:16:11.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弗洛也这么想
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.01,0:16:41.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会忘记你的 夏·多拉格尼尔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.48,0:16:46.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你 大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.70,0:16:59.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,消失了…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.59,0:17:09.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小型龙消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.13,0:17:11.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干掉了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.46,0:17:13.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然一头雾水 但看来是结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.84,0:17:17.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是夏哥 一定是夏哥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.06,0:17:23.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龙消失了…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.93,0:17:26.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功了呢 伽吉鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.19,0:17:29.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊…但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.19,0:17:31.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不爽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.45,0:17:39.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灭龙魔法师没有一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.49,0:17:42.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真正打倒了龙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.83,0:17:45.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真丢人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.79,0:17:48.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,枉被称为灭龙魔法师了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.96,0:17:52.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是那么强啊 所谓的龙…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.21,0:17:56.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怕阿库诺罗基亚会更强
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.01,0:17:59.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 现在别想了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.39,0:18:04.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 虽然没有胜利的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.52,0:18:07.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之战斗结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.19,0:18:14.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是胜利啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.03,0:18:17.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,守护了同伴们
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.17,0:18:34.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我认识的罗格
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.34,0:18:36.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会成为「你」的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.17,0:18:39.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,影子…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.09,0:18:39.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.22,0:18:44.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,影子…想要吞噬我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.85,0:18:47.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多少次 多少次地缠上我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.23,0:18:56.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后在失去弗洛的那天 我与影子成为了一体
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.82,0:18:58.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弗洛不会死
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.28,0:18:59.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是一年后
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.70,0:19:02.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要告诉「我」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.16,0:19:06.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一年后 一定要守护弗洛…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.54,0:19:14.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,——杀掉了弗洛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.07,0:20:19.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是…哪里…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.21,0:20:40.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 露西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.05,0:20:49.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点来这边
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.23,0:20:56.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家也都在哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.20,0:21:11.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来 继续冒险吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.96,0:21:17.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.16,0:21:52.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,泪水…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.96,0:22:07.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 露西
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.76,0:22:10.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么…情不自禁…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.51,0:22:15.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,555)}谢谢…
Comment: 0,0:00:00.06,0:00:00.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,==========Preview==========
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.24,0:23:59.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏 听我说哦 有大新闻哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.58,0:24:01.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了嘛哈比 慌慌张张的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.62,0:24:03.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作为拯救了王国的谢礼
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.17,0:24:05.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,国王大人好像要设宴招待我们呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.09,0:24:06.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.00,0:24:08.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是设在宫殿里的宴会
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.42,0:24:10.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定会有很多好吃的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.67,0:24:14.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比如照烧火焰的 又或是干蒸火焰之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.34,0:24:17.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个…恐怕有点难吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.60,0:24:19.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下一话 大型舞会
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.60,0:24:21.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有 烤全火好像也不错哦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.98,0:24:25.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说拿火焰当食材 到底是什么脑回路啊
